ation for jazz playing.", "doc_title": "Dave Liebman — Smithsonian Jazz Oral History", "collection": "si", "url": "https://amhistory.si.edu/jazz/Liebman-Dave/Liebman_Dave_Transcript.pdf"}, {"speaker": "Chazz Frichtel", "relation": "collaborated with", "confidence": 0.9, "evidence": "I was lucky enough to play most of the time Gerry was there... And we had a great band.", "doc_title": "Chazz Frichtel interviewed by Monk Rowe, Clinton, New York, June 13, 2016", "collection": "hamilton", "url": "https://litsdigital.hamilton.edu/collections/object/chazz-frichtel-interviewed-monk-rowe-clinton-new-york-june-13-2016"}]}